Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:34.88,0:01:37.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天似乎很冷啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:37.24,0:01:39.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然早了點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:39.40,0:01:40.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把被爐拿出來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:40.89,0:01:42.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被爐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:43.06,0:01:45.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請一定要拿出來啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:45.52,0:01:47.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想想…放在哪裡了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:48.00,0:01:50.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是我的房間吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:53.15,0:01:55.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被爐  被爐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:02.05,0:02:07.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,機械皇女克拉斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:08.42,0:02:09.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打擾了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:10.47,0:02:11.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.06,0:02:16.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們能來太感謝了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.83,0:02:20.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事  驅魔本來就是我的工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.93,0:02:23.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是真的有妖怪？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.82,0:02:26.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是不太清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.16,0:02:28.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是梨香當時嚇壞了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.24,0:02:40.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像沒什麼東西嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:40.47,0:02:42.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有妖怪嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.98,0:02:45.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的有的啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.58,0:02:49.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梨香  會不會是你學習過度太累了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.44,0:02:51.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.14,0:02:54.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種情節幾乎已經成規定了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.17,0:02:56.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妖怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.38,0:03:01.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然來了  喝杯茶吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.65,0:03:03.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  謝謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.41,0:03:05.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再來點上次的仙貝吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.62,0:03:07.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的有的啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.92,0:03:11.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是那張臉總覺得在哪裡見過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.28,0:03:16.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個孩子是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.67,0:03:18.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克拉斯殿下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.11,0:03:22.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在這種地方幹什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.03,0:03:25.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心…心…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.88,0:03:28.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.76,0:03:30.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好冷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.23,0:03:32.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就從冰箱裡出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.95,0:03:36.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來  喝點茶暖暖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.74,0:03:42.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,溫度測定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.28,0:03:44.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,華氏104.6度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.87,0:03:49.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成分分析完成還有55秒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.09,0:03:52.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個人怎麼回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.86,0:03:53.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.96,0:03:58.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼叫不知道  真田小姐是巴魯哈拉星的侍女長吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.68,0:04:01.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在八大皇家裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.08,0:04:04.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克拉斯殿下也幾乎不在別人面前露面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.24,0:04:07.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們這樣的人連見她都受到限制
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.16,0:04:12.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的確連我們皇女在國中也幾乎碰不到她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.42,0:04:14.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.67,0:04:18.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之  說難以理解也好不可思議也好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.17,0:04:21.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你給我解釋一下這一連串的事情吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.07,0:04:31.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.38,0:04:33.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在幹什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.83,0:04:35.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看看我看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.67,0:04:38.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然打擾十分抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.62,0:04:40.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是這是有原因的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.00,0:04:46.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,necomimi@tokinoyu…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.46,0:04:48.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個地址是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.20,0:04:53.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.88,0:04:57.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有信件  有信件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.86,0:04:59.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是真田
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.84,0:05:04.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請您告訴我那個原因
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.08,0:05:06.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.23,0:05:09.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要說的話會很長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.72,0:05:13.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個…那個…該怎麼說呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.19,0:05:16.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不  請別這麼說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.57,0:05:18.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來  節省時間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.45,0:05:20.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一點都不節省時間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.88,0:05:22.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不能說話了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.21,0:05:24.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.38,0:05:26.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你就直接說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.24,0:05:38.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好漂亮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.88,0:05:41.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底怎麼回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.54,0:05:43.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把我們拉到這種地方來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.69,0:05:45.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點說吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.32,0:05:49.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瓦露克蕾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.21,0:05:51.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.32,0:05:54.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海多拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.03,0:05:56.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.87,0:06:02.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和你們不一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.26,0:06:12.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不一樣  什麼不一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.13,0:06:17.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我雖然是巴魯哈拉星的皇女之一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.10,0:06:21.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我是機械
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.90,0:06:25.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看這個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.10,0:06:29.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有我的羽翼和大家不同
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.62,0:06:30.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的確
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.77,0:06:31.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.92,0:06:33.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是第一次聽說啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.98,0:06:35.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.63,0:06:36.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是當然的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.45,0:06:40.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為這是巴魯哈拉皇家的最高機密
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.38,0:06:41.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.99,0:06:45.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來的我小時候就死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.34,0:06:48.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,具體的事情我自己也不清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.46,0:06:53.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我的記憶都是被製造出來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.64,0:07:00.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如大家所知  八位皇女是巴魯哈拉星權力的象徵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.69,0:07:03.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任何一位都不能缺少
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.02,0:07:06.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以製造了我的身體
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.40,0:07:09.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並且移植了去世的皇女的資料
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.96,0:07:23.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我並不想知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.58,0:07:25.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是卻知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.06,0:07:28.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關於自己的真相
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.32,0:07:30.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個虛偽的真相
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.29,0:07:32.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在十天前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.27,0:07:37.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確認了我的設計上有致命的缺陷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.19,0:07:42.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,距離不可維護的動力爐停止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.27,0:07:43.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有三天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.21,0:07:47.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小克
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.79,0:07:54.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看  這個計數器顯示到0的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.90,0:07:57.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.96,0:07:59.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.05,0:08:05.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諸位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.87,0:08:06.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萊妮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.00,0:08:11.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴魯哈拉第一的期待之星萊妮殿下登場
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.04,0:08:15.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家原來在這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.99,0:08:18.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我兜遍整個街區了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.63,0:08:23.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個可是新買的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.23,0:08:26.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想讓大家快點欣賞一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.17,0:08:28.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克拉斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.81,0:08:32.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道克拉斯是機械人的事嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.04,0:08:35.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,機械人？  克拉斯？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.73,0:08:38.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種事擺明了是胡扯的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.36,0:08:43.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小克  振作點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.59,0:08:44.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要緊嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.41,0:08:47.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看  都是你說是胡扯什麼的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.70,0:08:49.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是失禮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.66,0:08:52.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說我在說謊羅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.43,0:08:55.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按你平時表現就是難以信任啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.34,0:08:57.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是失禮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.65,0:08:59.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.66,0:09:01.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克拉斯殿下  請振作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.78,0:09:04.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諸位別給她騙了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.15,0:09:08.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可真是個壞孩子啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.71,0:09:10.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs18}（伊拉伊薩：某超喜歡惡作劇的角色，不是My fair lady裡的那個……）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.71,0:09:10.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是伊拉伊薩啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.58,0:09:13.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是失禮  我是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.24,0:09:15.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  你閉嘴啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.46,0:09:29.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您醒了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.30,0:09:30.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.70,0:09:31.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.62,0:09:38.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些冷漠的言語使我的少女驅動產生反應
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.10,0:09:39.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才會變成那樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.89,0:09:41.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少女驅動？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.81,0:09:48.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  模仿人的內心使自己痛苦的程序
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.40,0:09:50.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真奇怪啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.30,0:09:56.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明不是人  明明不是真的痛苦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.19,0:10:00.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小克
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.47,0:10:05.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想請求和人先生一件事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.33,0:10:06.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.64,0:10:07.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有三天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.08,0:10:13.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想在這期間擁有美好的感情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.00,0:10:14.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美好的感情？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.29,0:10:18.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能讓我的少女驅動滿足的回憶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.95,0:10:21.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和理想的男友夢幻般的約會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.07,0:10:23.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,約會？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.58,0:10:25.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和和人？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.26,0:10:30.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在瓦露克蕾的結婚儀式上第一次見到他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.61,0:10:33.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好羨慕瓦露克蕾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.15,0:10:37.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能和這麼好的人相遇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.09,0:10:38.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小克
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.03,0:10:41.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  瓦露克蕾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.24,0:10:44.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒有想搶走你的他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.90,0:10:47.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我已經沒有時間了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.49,0:10:49.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也沒有別的人可以拜託了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.99,0:10:51.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.29,0:10:56.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了  和小克約會吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.62,0:10:58.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.52,0:11:01.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你  和人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.90,0:11:23.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在我只想沉浸在這份愉悅中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.95,0:11:31.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算明白這只是回路裡的電流信號
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.33,0:11:46.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是第二天了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.39,0:11:49.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克拉斯殿下那麼的高興
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.58,0:12:10.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從剛才開始你就在幹什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.03,0:12:14.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在調查阻止動力爐停止的方法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.22,0:12:17.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…得充電了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.65,0:12:19.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交給我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.29,0:12:31.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還能做這樣的事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.39,0:12:34.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我是機械
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.17,0:13:15.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柔和的顏色  清淡的氣味
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.94,0:13:17.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是地球上的大海
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.47,0:13:21.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果能帶著這份記憶消失的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.56,0:13:23.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已別無所求了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.10,0:13:25.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克拉斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.01,0:13:27.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來到地球太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.18,0:13:39.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諸位都在這裡啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.49,0:13:41.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還在晃來晃去啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.15,0:13:44.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家在看什麼呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.96,0:13:48.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個小子還在嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.55,0:13:52.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且還和我的和人先生如此的有氣氛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.70,0:13:54.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼這麼不要臉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.89,0:13:56.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點給我離遠點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.84,0:14:01.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克拉斯  振作點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:01.63,0:14:03.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萊妮殿下  太過分了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.45,0:14:04.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.59,0:14:06.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs18}（音羽：這個不知道出處……）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.59,0:14:06.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是音羽先生啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.26,0:14:07.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是失禮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.15,0:14:13.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不要緊了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.90,0:14:18.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  看樣子時間已到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.04,0:14:24.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和人先生  諸位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.20,0:14:27.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要說永別了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.98,0:14:29.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.21,0:14:35.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瓦露克蕾  要和和人先生永遠恩愛啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.14,0:14:36.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小克
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.42,0:14:40.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要連我的份也一起幸福
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.25,0:14:42.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們約好了哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.32,0:14:46.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請等一下  一定有什麼辦法的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.89,0:14:47.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.97,0:14:53.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了  不用了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.01,0:15:14.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,機能停止還有120秒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.24,0:15:16.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.51,0:16:05.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,機能停止還有90秒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:07.32,0:16:09.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,漸漸冷卻的熱流啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.60,0:16:11.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原子流啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.93,0:16:14.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請重新燃起生命之火
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.18,0:16:16.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,流遍鋼鐵的身軀吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.08,0:16:36.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會  為什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.50,0:16:37.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瓦露克蕾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.71,0:16:44.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.47,0:16:47.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進入最終倒數
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.42,0:16:50.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,10…9…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.84,0:16:52.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點想點辦法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.37,0:17:08.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來不及了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.31,0:17:11.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,4…3…2…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.26,0:17:14.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克拉斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.71,0:17:35.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克拉斯…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.24,0:18:01.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還活著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.29,0:18:05.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇跡  這是奇跡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.22,0:18:09.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相信奇跡  思念會傳達的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.64,0:18:13.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個是瓦露克蕾的力量嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.80,0:18:16.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  我想不是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:16.91,0:18:20.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  克拉斯是機械的事是？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.80,0:18:23.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我都說了是胡扯的了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.96,0:18:25.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是這麼回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.70,0:18:28.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的心真的是機械的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.98,0:18:30.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs18}（波庫：某穿青蛙衣的奇怪生物）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.98,0:18:30.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  波庫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.87,0:18:31.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,波庫是？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.21,0:18:33.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.91,0:18:35.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  波庫…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.68,0:18:37.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.71,0:18:40.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙以前就是這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.36,0:18:45.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直和她是同學所以知道的很清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.31,0:18:47.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你一開始就說嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:47.73,0:18:48.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說過了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.82,0:18:52.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰叫你平時亂說話搞得別人信不過你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.25,0:18:53.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是就是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.24,0:18:54.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是失禮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.81,0:19:04.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次又是怎麼回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:04.22,0:19:07.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正又是收到別的什麼電波了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:10.75,0:19:14.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出現問題  請重新啟動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.54,0:19:18.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有保存的程序全部會被清除
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.68,0:19:22.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你給我適可而止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.85,0:19:25.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.05,0:19:28.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對啊  就是剛剛的角度  海多拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.48,0:19:30.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼跟什麼嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:34.81,0:19:36.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎光臨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:36.83,0:19:38.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩人份
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:43.84,0:19:45.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天大家真是夠嗆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.27,0:19:48.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是累死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:48.06,0:19:51.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼巴魯哈拉的人都是些怪人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.75,0:19:53.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能我道歉也沒什麼用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.88,0:19:55.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過真的是抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.98,0:19:57.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.49,0:20:01.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從小時候起就被她煩死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.09,0:20:04.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說自己是機器人  宇宙人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:04.75,0:20:07.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宇宙人也沒說錯吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:08.12,0:20:10.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之她就是這麼不知所謂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:10.97,0:20:15.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我覺得比起克拉斯真的死了現在這樣好多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:16.51,0:20:19.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瓦露也希望小克活著好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:20.69,0:20:23.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主殿下  您多善良啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:29.61,0:20:33.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小克  已經到巴魯哈拉星了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:33.60,0:20:36.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她回去了也算鬆口氣了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:36.52,0:20:38.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說的一點沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.26,0:20:39.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  你也給我回去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:39.78,0:20:41.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.65,0:20:43.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次什麼時候才能再見面呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.12,0:20:45.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:13.16,0:21:16.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚上好  明天的天氣預報
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:16.88,0:21:18.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先是北海道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:26.73,0:21:30.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒有回去啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:31.56,0:21:32.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:32.66,0:21:33.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:36.40,0:21:38.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五百元
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:38.15,0:21:41.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都這時代了她居然還有這個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:42.21,0:21:43.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,短期的房租
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:43.90,0:21:45.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請收下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:51.41,0:21:52.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:54.29,0:21:58.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你都霸佔了別人的房間了  能不能別再自說自話的燒水了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:58.47,0:22:00.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  克拉斯殿下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:01.16,0:22:02.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您藏身藏的太漂亮了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:03.22,0:22:04.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到達沸點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:05.10,0:22:07.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,華氏212度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:42.27,0:23:43.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是海多拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:43.42,0:23:45.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克拉斯那個樣子真的抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:45.78,0:23:47.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都很吃驚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:47.67,0:23:49.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是什麼都不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:49.71,0:23:53.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為巴魯哈拉皇家也不願意說起克拉斯的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:53.27,0:23:55.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最高機密嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:55.02,0:23:56.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難怪啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:56.90,0:23:59.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話先說在前頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:59.12,0:24:00.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下周還要厲害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:01.42,0:24:03.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集  電波皇女克拉斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:03.86,0:24:07.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做好心理準備哦
